FROM title t, movie_companies mc, cast_info ci
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.company_id  <  3685 AND mc.company_type_id  >  1 AND ci.person_id  >  2840471 AND ci.role_id  =  3
